{"tid":530171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【朱經緯判囚】支持者罵官「死差婆」 警拉63歲女子涉藐視法庭","createTime":"2018-01-15T13:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T05:06:14.000Z","uid":47272,"like":191,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"16cd07711fcf8bb47ec3a5dc14a64c8673af6332","tid":530171,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:36:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180115&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57711895\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180115%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57711895&d=HW7sH8%2FlW9AFzI22btbTk3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=bd389c5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180115%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57711895&h=d19b6886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180115&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57711895</a><br />\n退休警司朱經緯在佔領期間以警棍擊傷途人罪成，被判囚3個月，一群支持朱的撐警人士發起遊行，並把矛頭直指印度出生的主審裁判官錢禮，在庭外罵她是「狗官」，甚至針對其族裔罵「死差婆」。警方於早前接獲相關轉介，指有人於1月3日在東區裁判法院外，涉嫌向司法人員作出不當及侮辱性言論，港島總區公眾活動調查組經調查後，今日在北角區拘捕一名63歲姓郭女子，涉嫌藐視法庭。被捕女子已獲准保釋候查，須於2月中旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥日前出席行會前曾表示，會堅定捍衞司法獨立，對於侮辱、恐嚇法官的行為不能接受，社會不會容忍，會依法處理。"},{"pid":"ab20713b161df67705691da86aeb6cfd2d218387","tid":530171,"uid":77196,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:40:29.000Z","msg":"廢老祭旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30134135ca887a01b9e09c15d1077bd99237789a","tid":530171,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ab20713b161df67705691da86aeb6cfd2d218387","tid":530171,"uid":77196,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:40:29.000Z","msg":"廢老祭旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:41:04.000Z","msg":"估判簽保守行為"},{"pid":"50d9fa64e1ad099c4e054c0c2a22a8775bc5c117","tid":530171,"uid":65892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab20713b161df67705691da86aeb6cfd2d218387","tid":530171,"uid":77196,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:40:29.000Z","msg":"廢老祭旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:41:04.000Z","msg":"是日好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fd183bfdd3c41c571864f8f850f156e30216a2","tid":530171,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:42:36.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70143f254932e59b99799136b99dbce7289da3c6","tid":530171,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58ac7394aa914c8acfdb1156c4057a0fe9c3a4e","tid":530171,"uid":43839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:51:45.000Z","msg":"判入獄先算啦~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a787d9e8fa7e98456dd3b63aea12ef87508127","tid":530171,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:52:39.000Z","msg":"On9廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6110eaa5c3f1604ecc8625719c110b98d3d17cfd","tid":530171,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:53:46.000Z","msg":"留名不提證供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a84bf09ca589b1bdc27d6f448fbbd8d41a3dde2","tid":530171,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:57:57.000Z","msg":"😂"},{"pid":"95aecd2531d908537566f281ae301759d4858be6","tid":530171,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:02:05.000Z","msg":"安全套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d5854736683f5cda5ac702971cd8d04df2a21e","tid":530171,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600ac3ca96b4e6adb0638254edafc3eaedea1358","tid":530171,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:04:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ecad6040734b96cbe4f988c1e4cf70dae80f2e4","tid":530171,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03fc2abd780d95057e02d92f0cd4781ffc51953","tid":530171,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:05:01.000Z","msg":"點止一個，成班喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370c66da8294e387d15e7c067695f1ae7ce63164","tid":530171,"uid":136994,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:08:13.000Z","msg":"會唔會係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2015年新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150423/19122537\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150423%2F19122537&d=HW7sH8%2FlW9AFzI22btbTk3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=5189566b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150423%2F19122537&h=bbf21c6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150423/19122537</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20150423/large/23la9p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20150423%2Flarge%2F23la9p2.jpg&h=0b98fc42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】保衛香港運動女成員去年在《城市論壇》直播前，向剛出獄的立法會議員梁國雄不斷喊叫「死監躉」，遭梁出手篤面頰後拍打梁的左肩。她昨被裁定普通襲擊罪成，裁判官斥責她出席論壇旨在羞辱不同政見人士，作惡意人身攻擊，為在場中學生樹立壞榜樣，行為應被譴責，判罰款3,000元。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「旨在羞辱不同政見人士」</strong><br />\n任僱傭中介公司文員的被告郭綺華（60歲）以往無案底，早前否認公眾地方擾亂秩序行為及普通襲擊兩罪受審。她自辯時曾指廣東人有習俗向剛出獄的親友送碌柚葉，她遂在案發日給梁送上碌柚葉「洗監躉味」。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官蘇惠德裁決時指被告不認識梁，施襲時沒攜帶碌柚葉，證供不盡不實，只為開脫。從錄影片段見到，梁轉身用手篤被告後沒繼續施襲，被告卻隨即打梁的肩膊，可見她是故意報復，並非自衞，裁定她普通襲擊罪成。<br />\n<br />\n不過，蘇官認為現場情況混亂與被告的行為沒直接關係，反而是因梁的舉動而起，故判她餘下一罪不成立。蘇官批評被告到場非為參與討論，旨在謾罵及羞辱不同政見人士，對他們作惡意人身攻擊，所作所為實給現場的中學生樹立壞榜樣，且妨礙節目進行，行為不僅不值得鼓勵，更應譴責。<br />\n<br />\n長毛因衝擊替補機制論壇判監四星期，去年7月6日出獄翌日出席《城市論壇》遭被告襲擊，事後跟被告同遭起訴。他涉嫌襲擊被告一案將於5月28日開審。<br />\n《城市論壇》主持人謝志峰昨到庭旁聽，在庭外遭數名被告的支持者包圍謾罵主持不公，愛港之聲主席高達斌見狀即勸止。謝指工作人員會繼續檢查入場人士的隨身物品，日後如有需要會增聘保安員維持秩序。"},{"pid":"5fde5d336ac53780501522a9146eb139db7d546c","tid":530171,"uid":35129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:08:15.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4adaf7da803866113b5427816800d001beb903a","tid":530171,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:11:02.000Z","msg":"恩將仇報呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83832c599560b96736e496eee312fb6462efde7","tid":530171,"uid":156162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:11:03.000Z","msg":"尼D人同當年文革紅衛兵冇分別"},{"pid":"9bd3ed9f97f014cd929e39410de794d9ce49be01","tid":530171,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:13:28.000Z","msg":"北角廢老區"},{"pid":"7802210732f9a8140568fd62762d505b11fefe00","tid":530171,"uid":113966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:24:22.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收得幾百做五毛狗 洗唔洗咁落力攪到要坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9badf798dfc93c1ad493632de6c4f69dbe82c5","tid":530171,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抵死"},{"pid":"fd1865d30fbc4d1a09cd0fae3b2ca7b0e938c8ca","tid":530171,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:36:16.000Z","msg":"還有黨呀"},{"pid":"5af7890c66157b51703d844a27cd8cb97081b5fe","tid":530171,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T14:42:45.000Z","msg":"種族歧視，可以坐牢"},{"pid":"e7ec82bcde7439240ee62f36cc143f3faa488edc","tid":530171,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"陪朱經緯一齊坐囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}